title: 2012–13 FK Sarajevo season
text: The 2012–2013 season was <a href="FK%20Sarajevo">FK Sarajevo</a>'s 13th (19th) in <a href="Bosnian%20Premier%20League">Bosnian Premier League</a>, 53rd consecutive season in the top flight and 65th season in <a href="History%20of%20FK%20Sarajevo">existence of the club</a>.
